This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.DL (Digital Libraries) as it deals with bibliometric data and matching algorithms to identify scholars with a Twitter account. Additionally, the paper also discusses the presence of scholars from different domains on Twitter, which could fall under sub-categories such as cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.CY (Computers and Society), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
